<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.5.3">
<l>niṉṟiṭun ticaikku naiyumeṉ ṟaṉṉaiya rumuṉitir.</l>
<l>kuṉṟa māṭat tirukkuṟuṅkuṭi nampiyai nāṉkaṇṭapiṉ</l>
<l>veṉṟi villun taṇṭum vāḷuñ cakkaramuñ caṅkamu</l>
<l>niṉṟu tōṉṟik kaṇṇuṇīṅkā neñcuḷḷu nīṅkāvē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“She stays put, subsides, languishes”, so you will all disapprove, mothers.</l>
<l>After I saw Nampi of Tirukkuṟuṅkuṭi with hill[-high] storied mansions,</l>
<l>the victorious bow, the staff, the sword, the discus and the conch</l>
<l>appear constantly, don’t depart from [my] eyes, don’t depart from my mind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
